			"body": "> Done! I did not test Android, only the joplin-desktop electron application on Linux.\r\n\r\nIf you don't want to go through all the process of building the mobile app, I can build an apk with your change for you (using the Joplin dev signing certificate). Would you be willing to test if the PQC TLS works on Android on a spare device / Android emulator if I provide the apk for you?\r\n\r\nIt doesn't matter so much if it doesn't actually work on Android, but I think it would be good to update the platforms which the fix addresses in the PR title accordingly if not, otherwise it is going to go in the changelog for all platforms and could be misleading.",
